---
---
<section id="about" class="section about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text-content">
        <span class="badge badge-maroon">Our Mission</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Built by Students, <br/>For the <span class="gradient-text-green">Elbi Community</span></h2>
        <p class="about-desc">
          uplb.tools is an independent, open-source organization founded by students from the University of the Philippines Los Baños. We build useful utilities that solve everyday student problems while establishing a premium learning hub for tech enthusiasts.
        </p>
        <p class="about-desc">
          Whether it’s finding an empty classroom or simulating your path to graduating with honors, our projects are built to support every student's academic journey.
        </p>
        
        <div class="stats-row">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <h3 class="gradient-text-maroon">2+</h3>
            <p>Live Tools</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <h3 class="gradient-text-green">100%</h3>
            <p>Open Source</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <h3 class="gradient-text-maroon">0</h3>
            <p>Ads or Tracking</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-cards-content">
        <div class="card value-card">
          <div class="value-icon-wrapper red">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M22 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h5l2 3h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path>
              <line x1="12" y1="11" x2="12" y2="17"></line>
              <line x1="9" y1="14" x2="15" y2="14"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="value-text">
            <h3>Student Utilities</h3>
            <p>We build tools that address daily student pain points, such as room lookups and grade mapping, streamlining academic workflows.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card value-card">
          <div class="value-icon-wrapper green">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"></polygon>
              <polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"></polyline>
              <polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="value-text">
            <h3>Creative Sandbox</h3>
            <p>We serve as an active sandbox and mentoring environment for devs, UX/UI designers, and writers looking to gain real project experience.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card value-card">
          <div class="value-icon-wrapper red">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
              <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="value-text">
            <h3>Privacy & Open Source</h3>
            <p>No ads, no trackers, no monetization. All code is public, and student data remains completely local to their device.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(13, 17, 34, 0.3) 100%);
  }
  
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.95fr 1.05fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  
  .about-desc {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .stats-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .stat-item h3 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  
  .stat-item p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  
  .about-cards-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .value-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .value-icon-wrapper {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .value-icon-wrapper.red {
    background: rgba(184, 29, 64, 0.1);
    color: #ff5e83;
    border: 1px solid rgba(184, 29, 64, 0.2);
  }
  
  .value-icon-wrapper.green {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
    color: #34d399;
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
  }
  
  .value-text h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .value-text p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3.5rem;
    }
    
    .stats-row {
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
